OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGoldman Sachs removes      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbankers' bonus limit       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The investment bank Goldman Sachs has  
OL,6, become the first to remove its cap on  
OL,7, bankers' bonuses following changes to  
OL,8, UK laws introduced last year.          
OL,10,FThe bank said this would give "greater 
OL,11,Fflexibility" and was closer to what    
OL,12,Fhappens in other big financial centres 
OL,13,Fsuch as Singapore and New York.        
OL,15,FBonuses were limited to twice basic pay
OL,16,Fin a move introduced by the EU in 2014.
OL,18,FOther big banks are thought to be      
OL,19,Fconsidering a similar moves.           
